35 void MainWindow::displayPointCloud(QString url, QString name)
36 {
37  pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGB>::Ptr tmpCloud (new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGB>);
38  if(pcl::io::loadPCDFile<pcl::PointXYZRGB>(url.toUtf8().constData(), *tmpCloud) == -1){
